&kp LS(LEFT_GUI)  &kp DEL  &kp PG_UP   &kp CAPS  &kp PG_DN  &kp LPAR    &kp RPAR  &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &trans
